    <item>
      <title>南非新政府立法者重启支出法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/south-africa-lawmakers-revive-spending-bill-under-new-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非议会在新政府成立以来的首次投票中同意恢复一项法案，该法案允许国库向各部委发放截至2025年3月的年度资金，以履行其职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/south-africa-lawmakers-revive-spending-bill-under-new-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 15:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院授予特朗普“利剑”以削减拜登的气候规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/supreme-court-gives-trump-sword-to-slash-biden-s-climate-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果特朗普在十一月获胜，法院推翻雪佛龙原则将有助于他放松环境法规。]]></description>
